184491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:21:18.000Z","msg":"我以為你講天水連線搵果個添<br />\n果個要上庭 但唔關出去發夢被拉嘅事<br />\n係佢話佢以為條仔用佢名借咗錢<br />\n被人告咋<br />\n佢就周圍同人講要上庭 又冇交代係佢以前條仔借落人地錢，俾人告....<br />\n元朗d黃店以為佢俾黑警告<br />\n走去俾飯劵、請佢做pt......<br />\n佢四圍同人講d利益歸自己嘅嘢<br />\nPs我係一手，佢自己講俾以前條仔用名借錢要上庭（但故事唔合邏輯，似作故仔....果d,點知佢就不斷係fb到同人講要上庭又冇講清楚咩事....伏到爆）"},{"pid":"b9b079840d650b89c7120d12a528ba4ca29c3ecd","tid":2156652,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好有事啊"},{"pid":"e472f18fc150c6091129a7535f23a5d86fd36947","tid":2156652,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc62d830b20e6c2e030b9556be0db6baa273acf","tid":2156652,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d13f0cfcdf1e6e1a8be76b9f0da8a3866fbaaea","tid":2156652,"uid":112878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"458836f191a6417c7d97584e7b8643c7fb07a710","tid":2156652,"uid":322110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:24:42.000Z","msg":"救人丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到人無事為止！"},{"pid":"8de4b97538f58464554f1a75a52789372177486f","tid":2156652,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}